keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein sent an email on January 26, 2010, stating he would 'stay in one of the apts'.
The email includes a confidentiality footer claiming the communication may be attorney-client privileged and is the property of Jeffrey Epstein.
The document is identified as part of the Epstein case records with identifiers SDNY_FR_00000023 and EFTA00095347.
